---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Infinite Canvas" activeItem="/">
  <!-- header slot-->
  <header slot="header" class="text-center p-4">
    <h1>Infinite Canvas</h1>
    <p class="font-serif">New tools that work the way we think</p>
  </header>

  <!-- default slot -->
  <section class="text-center p-4">
    <h2>Meet the apps paving the way</h2>
    <div>- placeholder for list of apps -</div>
    <a href="/gallery">Browse the app gallery →</a>
  </section>

  <section class="p-4">
    <div>
      <h2 class="sans-40">We think spatially</h2>
      <p>
        People have been organizing and processing information spatially for
        centuries, whether it be with notes in a notebook or bulletin boards
        with stickies and photos.
      </p>
      <p>
        This type of work uses a parts of our brain dedicated to spatial
        navigation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Software that mirrors how we think</h2>
      <p>
        Traditional tools like text editors and presentation software have
        linear interfaces that mimic their output.
      </p>
      <p>
        Infinite canvas tools instead embrace the messy, circuitous paths we
        take when brainstorming, sketching and distilling ideas.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <secion>
    <h2 class="text-center">What makes an infinite canvas?</h2>
    <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 p-4 gap-4">
      <li>
        <h3>Expansiveness</h3>
        <p>
          A seemingly limitless canvas allows for free thinking and creation
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Zoom</h3>
        <p>
          Different zoom levels mimic stepping into and stepping away in the
          real world
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Direct manipulation</h3>
        <p>
          Direct manipulation of objects including freeform movement, editing
          and duplication
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Collaboration</h3>
        <p>
          Real time collaboration combines the best of software and working
          together in person
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </secion>
  <section class="text-center p-4">
    <h2>History</h2>
    <p>There is a long lineage of software built around an infinite canvas.</p>
    <ol class="grid grid-cols-4 p-4 gap-4">
      <li>
        <time datetime="1963">1963</time>
        <h3>Sketchpad</h3>
      </li>
      <li>
        <time datetime="1987">1987</time>
        <h3>Adobe Illustrator</h3>
      </li>
      <li>
        <time datetime="2006">2006</time>
        <h3>Blender node editor</h3>
      </li>
      <li>
        <time datetime="2016">2016</time>
        <h3>Figma</h3>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <a href="/history">Browse the timeline →</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
